# codicon.css

A lightweight CSS utility repository for managing and deploying custom codicon formatting styles.

## Getting Started

Follow these steps to link your local project files to this GitHub repository and push your initial codebase.

### 1. Link your local repository to GitHub
Initialize your local Git repository if you haven't already, then point it to this remote location:
```bash
git remote add origin [https://github.com/Cleanskiier27/codicon.css.git](https://github.com/Cleanskiier27/codicon.css.git)
